::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor freezes as he hears the bushes rustle behind him, the dumb bug 
frowning. He turns around, taking a few steps toward the source of the 
ruffling. Holding his gun ready, he carefully aproaches Tails' location.

"Show yourself!" he says, ready to kill.
